Context()->texStrings;
BEGIN_TEXT

Convert the exponential equation to the form \( Q = ab^{t} \).
In the blanks, give the corresponding values for the values of \(a\)
and \(b\) once you have rewritten the formula.
$PAR
\( Q = $a e^{$k t} \)
$BR
\( a = \) \{ ans_rule(10) \}
$BR
\( b = \) \{ ans_rule(10) \}

END_TEXT
